                    <h3 class=" green" style="margin-top:20px" data-aos="fade-right">
                        Am I eligible?

                    </h3>

                    <p class="text-black" data-aos="fade-right">
                        <strong> 1.Childcare requirement:</strong>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled  primary mb-0 text-black">
                            <!--<li><a href="#"><span class="icon-arrow-up"></span></a></li>-->
                            <li>
                                &bull; Taking care of your child in any event 2 evenings or 14% for each fortnight.
                            </li>
                            <li>&bull; Need to pay for any approved child care service.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-black" data-aos="fade-right">
                        <strong>
                            2.Residency requirements (meet one of the following
                        </strong>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled  primary mb-0 text-black">
                            <!--<li><a href="#"><span class="icon-arrow-up"></span></a></li>-->
                            <li>
                                &bull; You or your accomplice must be living in Australia and any one of you holds Australian citizenship or one of the following visa,
                                a permanent visa, a Special Category visa, a certain temporary visa type.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                &bull; you or your accomplice are an understudy from abroad, supported by the Australian Government to concentrate in Australia .
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                &bull; you're in difficulty, or unique conditions apply.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-black" data-aos="fade-right">
                        <strong>
                            3.Child relevant requirements:
                        </strong>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled  primary mb-0 text-black">
                            <!--<li><a href="#"><span class="icon-arrow-up"></span></a></li>-->
                            <li>
                                &bull; Strictly follow the Childhood schedule published by the Department of Health’s National Immunisation Program Schedule as well as the current Australian Immunisation Handbook.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                &bull; Apply for a medical exemption  on the Australian Immunisation Register (AIR).
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                &bull; Your child is under 13 or 14 to 18 with disability.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-black" data-aos="fade-right">
                        <strong>
                            4.Requirements for additional subsidy (meet one of the following):
                        </strong>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled  primary mb-0 text-black">
                            <!--<li><a href="#"><span class="icon-arrow-up"></span></a></li>-->
                            <li>
                                &bull;  You are a grandparent.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                &bull;  You are transitioning to work.

                            </li>
                            <li>
                                &bull;  You are experiencing temporary financial hardship.
                            </li>
                        </ul>


